				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" markup="html"/>
				<text><![CDATA[d. The company has absolute liberty to call upon the Borrower/s to comply with and pay all the statutory payments under Income Tax Act, Finance Act (Service Tax) and such other acts, as may be applicable to the borrower or has to be complied with by the Borrower from time to time, and all such contributions have to be made by the Borrower/s out of their own funds other than the Loan extended by the Company and provide proof of the same when asked for by the Company.]]></text>
